{"tid":1534665,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8．31涉暴動被告出院提堂　准保釋不得離港","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:32:01.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"74d88eab1a2ab61ebca17fdd54ce4fdfe67b5f96","tid":1534665,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"反修訂《逃犯條例》風波不息，民陣8．31遊行集會不獲警方批准，大批示威者仍走上街頭，演變為警民衝突。當日被捕的16人被控暴動罪，其中一名原本留院的被告，今（3日）出院並到庭應訊，他獲准以5000元保釋金、不准離港等條件保釋外出。<br />\n<br />\n鄒咏霖（23歲）被控於2019年8月31日，在銅鑼灣百德新街一帶，連同其他人參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至10月21日再訊。裁判官准被告以5000元保釋金、不准離港、交出旅遊證件、每周到警署報到一次、居住報稱地址的條件保釋外出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190903/s00001/1567484599222/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%918-31%e6%b6%89%e6%9a%b4%e5%8b%95%e8%a2%ab%e5%91%8a%e5%87%ba%e9%99%a2%e6%8f%90%e5%a0%82-%e5%87%86%e4%bf%9d%e9%87%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%be%97%e9%9b%a2%e6%b8%af\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190903%2Fs00001%2F1567484599222%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%25918-31%25e6%25b6%2589%25e6%259a%25b4%25e5%258b%2595%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e5%2591%258a%25e5%2587%25ba%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%258f%2590%25e5%25a0%2582-%25e5%2587%2586%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258b%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%25be%2597%25e9%259b%25a2%25e6%25b8%25af&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFGE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=b2bc90ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190903%2Fs00001%2F1567484599222%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%25918-31%25e6%25b6%2589%25e6%259a%25b4%25e5%258b%2595%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e5%2591%258a%25e5%2587%25ba%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%258f%2590%25e5%25a0%2582-%25e5%2587%2586%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258b%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%25be%2597%25e9%259b%25a2%25e6%25b8%2